Study Title: Validation of RNA-seq 1: Celecoxib, Rofecoxib Chronically Treated Mice, with IL1beta
Study Description: Metabolite profiling of urine, plasma, aorta, liver, heart, kidney and skeletal muscle. Treated with Celecoxib (100 mg/kg/day), Rofecoxib (50 mg/kg/day), or normal chow for three weeks. Mice were injected with 500ng of IL-1 beta 4hrs before sacrificing.
